These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: lemon, nectarine, cucumber, corn
Nationality: american, polish, malaysian, australian
1. Nationality:polish is on the left of Nationality:american##1
2. Food:lemon == Nationality:australian##1
3. Nationality:malaysian is on the right of Nationality:american##1
4. Food:nectarine is on the left of Nationality:australian##1
5. Food:corn is on the left of Nationality:american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | corn | cucumber | nectarine | lemon   |
| Nationality   | polish  | american     | malaysian   | australian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: rock-climbing, magic-tricks, collecting, traveling
Sport: biathlon, cricket, rowing, water-polo
1. Hobby:traveling == Sport:cricket##1
2. Hobby:rock-climbing is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:magic-tricks is on the right of Hobby:traveling##1
4. Hobby:traveling is on the right of Sport:rowing##1
5. Sport:cricket is on the left of Sport:biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | collecting | traveling | magic-tricks | rock-climbing    |
| Sport   | rowing    | cricket      | biathlon | water-polo |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
