2. Hobby:dancing == Movie-Genre:disaster##1
3. Movie-Genre:satire is on the far right##1
4. Movie-Genre:martial-arts is on the right of Hobby:hiking##1
5. Hobby:drawing is on the left of Movie-Genre:satire##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | dancing | hiking | drawing   | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | comedy | martial-arts | satire         |

