3. Movie-Genre:western == Hobby:hiking##1
4. Movie-Genre:western is on the left of Movie-Genre:romance##1
5. Movie-Genre:romance is on the left of Hobby:filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
